        name - name of the parameter (without delimiter)

      • Parameter

        public Parameter(java.lang.String name,
                 java.lang.String prefix,
                 java.lang.String sufix,
                 java.lang.String description,
                 boolean required,
                 int minValues,
                 int maxValues,
                 java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> values,
                 ParamExecutor executor,
                 int executorIndex)
        Create a new CLA parameter
        Parameters:
        name - name of the parameter (without delimiter)
        prefix - prefix of the parameter
        sufix - sufix of the parameter
        description - description of the parameter
        required - optional or required
        minValues - minimum number of values
        maxValues - maximum number of values
        values - collection of fixed values for this param
        executor - command to execute with this param or null
        executorIndex - execution index, bigger value, later execution
